                                                    signs and symptoms of GI ulceration.</li>
                                                <li>Diclofenac + pentoxifylline : The use of pentoxifylline has been
                                                    associated with bleeding
                                                    and/or prolongation in prothrombin time. </li>
                                                <li>Monitoring of INR</li>
                                            </ul>
