                                            <ul>
                                                <li>
                                                    <b>Max:</b> 15 mg/day PO for tablets and oral suspension; 10 mg/day
                                                    PO for capsules.
                                                </li>
                                                <li><b>Hepatic:</b> No dose adjustment is needed in mild to moderate
                                                    hepatic impairment.
                                                    Meloxicam is not recommended in patients with severe hepatic
