                                                <li>If patient is on mechanical ventilator …. Use Fentanyl, Morphine
                                                </li>
                                                <li>If patient Extubated with Moderate to severe non-neuropathic pain
                                                    ... Use IV fentanyl,
                                                    Morphine
                                                </li>
                                                <li>If patient recieves intermittent bolus opioid dose ( Moderate pain,
                                                    Analgesia before
