                                                <li><b>Hepatic:</b> Data not available</li>
                                                <li><b>Renal:</b> Data not available</li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <h4>Dosing for mechanically ventilated adults:</h4>
                                            <p class="card-p">
                                                Iv dose initial 0.1 to 0.5 mg/kg bolus followed by 0.2 to 0.5 mg/kg/hr
